<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē tarkara<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>drāruṇaparigaṇitē śrāvaṇē kṛṣṇapakṣē dha
<lb n="2" break="no"/><supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>māhē jīvavārē hariśikharipatē<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> sannidhau dhupakālē <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> puṇyāptyai cāma
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rasya pratidinamadadāddharanāyāpi tōdyē patraśrīdā<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>mmadāsaprabu
<lb n="4" break="no"/>varatanayō visvanathō vadanya[ḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>*] śakavaruṣaṁbulu 1296 gunē
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṁṭi śrāvaṇa kṛṣṇa dasamiyu guruvāramunāṁḍu kaḷiṁgaparīkṣa
<lb n="6"/>pātraśrīdarmmadāsajīyyana Adikāramaṁdu vīri koḍukulu <unclear>pa</unclear>ṁḍḍalē
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ṁka kaḷiṁgamāji visvanādajīyyana tanaku nabhiṣṭā<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>tthasidiga śrī
<lb n="8" break="no"/>narasiṁhanāthuni sannidhini Ubhayadupalanu cāmarapaṭṭanu śrībha
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṁḍaramaṁdu padmanidhigaṁdamāḍalu 10 peṭṭi reṁḍu nibaṁdālū
<lb n="10"/>vṛtigāṁ baḍasi sānulaṁdu narasiṁhamukhari manumaṟālu bā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>lasarasvati purasāni saṁpradāyamaṁdu samudrataṁttāsāni
<lb n="12"/>manmāṟālu kuppāsānikinni Ācaṁdrārkastahigaṁ beṭṭenu vī
<lb n="13" break="no"/>riddaṟunnu Ī prasa<supplied reason="omitted">da</supplied>mu nelapaḍi Appalu viḍiyalu Eṁḍa
<lb n="14" break="no"/>dijītamu Enimidi sinnālu 8 paṟukalu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> [Ī]ṁtavaṭṭunu
<lb n="15"/>bhujiṁci koluvaṁgalāru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmuvu śrīvaiṇava rakṣa <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
<lb n="16"/>śatruṇapakṛtō dharmma palanīyō mā<unclear>nīṣi</unclear>bhi<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> <unclear>śa</unclear>trurava hi śatrusya
<lb n="17" break="no"/>dharma satru na kasyacit <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī śrī śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> vīri dattamu cāmara O 1 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

